arStrings.szText: "Got any more Overseer relics to track down?"
In fact, I do. There's another artifact I've heard of, but haven't yet had the chance to pursue -  the cleaver of an Overseer.
As if sharing a secret; slightly gleeful/hopefuly
This guy was a real butcher, and he eventually passed his skill with a blade along with the cleaver itself to his daughter, Khaliun.
In awe; telling a story of someone he finds interesting
Following Khaliun's death and suspecting a darkness in the cleaver, the mages managed to get ahold of it and lock it away in the Whispering Vault.
Slightly gleeful, while foreboding. Telling the player a tale
The vault was long since raided and the mages driven out, but I've hope it's still buried in one of the chests therein.
Informative, with a bit of hopeful anticipation
